Text:
Sigh. If this were real, would it not have a link to the website of the people who made it? Would it not have a verifiable MD5 hash of the file? Would "Anonymous" be the poster?

No thank you. I can get malware anywhere. I need not be tricked by you. (This may be clean, but posting this like this is a dead giveaway of malware.)

You may as well give up on this one and try again with proper information if this is legitimate.
Awesome game. That Nostalgia. Is clean, ignore OmniNegro for this torrent specifically, but take his advice seriously. Be alert.
